link: Seiichi Manyama, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..152
mathematica: A[n_] :=  Sum[d^(3*d + 1), {d, Divisors[n]}]; a[n_]:=If[n==0, 1, -(1/n)*Sum[A[k]*a[n - k], {k, n}]]; Table[a[n], {n, 0, 12}] (* _Indranil Ghosh_, Mar 11 2017 *)
